init_text:
Is Listening to a Book Just as Good as Reading It?

Do you listen to audiobooks? What are the benefits, in your opinion, of listening instead of reading? Are there advantages to reading that cannot be gained by listening? Which method do you prefer? Why?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I don't want to hear what they are listening to.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Second, you have to be able to listen to the book at a certain pace.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Third, I don't like the way audiobooks sound.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I can see it in my head much easier when I read.
